    Guest - Class in com.erahotel.era_backend.entity
    Guest Entity class that represents a Guest obj in the Era Hotel database This stores personal details such as name, email and phone Also stores a List of strings which are reservationId's stored in guestReservations the logic for appending a reservationId into the list is defined in the frontend within BookingForm.jsx
